<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg%20xmlns='http%3A//www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%2040%2040'><path%20d='M4%2021%20A16%2015%200%200%201%2036%2021%20Z'%20fill='%2310233F'/><rect%20x='9'%20y='21'%20width='4.4'%20height='6'%20rx='1.6'%20fill='%231D5BD8'/><rect%20x='17.8'%20y='21'%20width='4.4'%20height='10'%20rx='1.6'%20fill='%231D5BD8'/><rect%20x='26.6'%20y='21'%20width='4.4'%20height='14'%20rx='1.6'%20fill='%231D5BD8'/></svg>">
<title>회원 가입 — Team DIN 보장분석기 리포트 생성기</title>
<style>
  :root{--ink:#10233F;--paper:#F6F7F9;--card:#FFFFFF;--line:#E3E7EE;--sub:#5B6B82;--ok:#1D5BD8;--gap:#C93030}
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  body{font-family:-apple-system,"Pretendard",sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0F3068 0%,#1A4B8C 50%,#0F3068 100%);color:var(--ink);margin:0;padding:0;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
  .split{display:flex;width:100%;height:100vh;max-height:100vh}
  .hero{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-start;padding:60px 80px;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0F3068 0%,#1A4B8C 50%,#0F3068 100%)}
  .hero h2{font-size:42px;font-weight:900;margin:0 0 24px 0;line-height:1.2}
  .hero p{font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.7}
  .form-box{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:48px;background:var(--paper)}
  .form-container{width:100%;max-width:380px}
  .brand-lockup{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin-bottom:28px}
  .brand-lockup .wordmark{font-family:"Noto Serif KR",serif;font-weight:700;font-size:17px;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-.01em}
  h1{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 8px 0;color:var(--ink)}
  .sub{color:var(--sub);font-size:14px;margin:0 0 28px 0}
  .form-group{margin-bottom:18px}
  label{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 8px 0;color:var(--ink)}
  input{width:100%;padding:14px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;font-size:15px;font-family:inherit;background:var(--card);color:var(--ink);transition:all .2s}
  input:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--ok);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(29,91,216,.1)}
  button{margin-top:28px;width:100%;padding:14px;border:none;border-radius:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1D5BD8 0%,#1a4fa8 100%);color:#fff;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(29,91,216,.25)}
  button:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(29,91,216,.35)}
  button:active{transform:translateY(0)}
  .err{margin:16px 0;padding:14px 16px;background:#FBEDED;color:var(--gap);border-radius:8px;font-size:13.5px;border-left:4px solid var(--gap)}
  .footer{margin-top:24px;text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:var(--sub)}
  .footer a{color:var(--ok);font-weight:700;text-decoration:none}
  .footer a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
  @media (max-width:768px){
    .split{flex-direction:column;height:auto}
    .hero{padding:40px 20px;min-height:300px}
    .hero h2{font-size:32px}
    .form-box{padding:36px 20px}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="split">
  <div class="hero">
    <h2>전문가와 함께하는<br>보험 관리</h2>
    <p>Team DIN의 맞춤형 분석으로 당신에게 필요한 보험 보장을 정확하게 파악하세요.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="form-box">
    <div class="form-container">
      <div class="brand-lockup">{{ logo_mark|safe }}<span class="wordmark">Team DIN</span></div>
      <h1>회원 가입</h1>
      <p class="sub">계정을 생성하여 시작하세요</p>
      {% if error %}<div class="err">{{ error }}</div>{% endif %}
      <form method="post" action="/signup">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">이름</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="홍길동" value="{{ name or '' }}">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="phone">휴대폰번호</label>
          <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required placeholder="010-1234-5678" value="{{ phone or '' }}">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
          <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required placeholder="6자 이상">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="password_confirm">비밀번호 확인</label>
          <input type="password" id="password_confirm" name="password_confirm" required placeholder="비밀번호 재입력">
        </div>
        <button type="submit">회원 가입하기</button>
      </form>
      <div class="footer">
        이미 계정이 있으신가요? <a href="/login">로그인</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script>
  function formatPhone(digits) {
    digits = digits.slice(0, 11);
    if (digits.startsWith('02')) {
      if (digits.length <= 2) return digits;
      if (digits.length <= 5) return digits.slice(0, 2) + '-' + digits.slice(2);
      if (digits.length <= 9) return digits.slice(0, 2) + '-' + digits.slice(2, 5) + '-' + digits.slice(5);
      return digits.slice(0, 2) + '-' + digits.slice(2, 6) + '-' + digits.slice(6, 10);
    }
    if (digits.length <= 3) return digits;
    if (digits.length <= 6) return digits.slice(0, 3) + '-' + digits.slice(3);
    if (digits.length <= 10) return digits.slice(0, 3) + '-' + digits.slice(3, 6) + '-' + digits.slice(6);
    return digits.slice(0, 3) + '-' + digits.slice(3, 7) + '-' + digits.slice(7, 11);
  }
  const phoneInput = document.getElementById('phone');
  phoneInput.addEventListener('input', () => {
    const digits = phoneInput.value.replace(/\D/g, '');
    phoneInput.value = formatPhone(digits);
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
